            <title>[CAMEL-8584] Circuit breaker does not honour halfOpenAfter period</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-8584</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The CircuitBreakerLoadBalancer will always switch to a half-open state immediately after the first rejected message instead of honouring the halfOpenAfter period.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s due to the failed message count getting reset in the rejectExchange method:&lt;br/&gt;
